<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT4">
<l>kēṭkayā ṉuṟṟa tuṇṭu kēḻalā yulakaṅ koṇṭa</l>
<l>pūkkeḻu vaṇṇa ṉāraip pōtarak kaṉavil kaṇṭu</l>
<l>vākkiṉāl karuman taṉṉāl maṉattiṉāl cirattai taṉṉāl</l>
<l>vēṭkaimī tūra vāṅki viḻuṅkiṉēṟ kiṉiya vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is something I have to ask; seeing in a dream as [he] came,</l>
<l>Him the bright hue of a flower, who took [up] the earth as a boar,</l>
<l>Through speech, through deeds, through the heart, through faith,</l>
<l>For me who seizes and devours [him] as desire mounts, [what] is the sweet[est] way?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
